casebody.data:
Moones MELLOULI, applicant,
v.
Loretta E. LYNCH, Attorney General. No. 15A137. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 2, 2015.

*437Joint motion to vacate the Court's order of August 21, 2015, granting the application for stay granted. The stay of proceedings heretofore issued by the Court on August 21, 2015, is hereby vacated.
